{"tid":1961381,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵返夢入面個男仔","createTime":"2020-04-06T18:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T18:39:04.000Z","uid":49847,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf3f1683176fb0bcd5715fdda5bcf8715ff775e4","tid":1961381,"uid":49847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:23:40.000Z","msg":"發左個好長既夢<br />\n有2個Ending<br />\n<br />\n第一個係我上左個唔識既男主角屋企 然後佢推我 屌左<br />\n一齊生活左一陣<br />\n跟住同佢屋企人食飯 <br />\n佢襯佢老豆入左廚房果陣話佢老豆試過斬佢隻腳 <br />\n然後個男仔就拎左把刀出黎 愈放愈埋 最後俾佢同佢老豆殺左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第2個結局係 食完飯佢成家人第日就搬走左<br />\n<br />\n訓醒好有失戀Feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />究竟你係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想搵返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef554469c8634ee71321f3f35d6915b723505cb","tid":1961381,"uid":49847,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:24:02.000Z","msg":"第一次開膠Post唔知有冇人覆 有就用不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84f01632b287292f49f84ba1de0d7e793c2fc89","tid":1961381,"uid":333451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:24:45.000Z","msg":"Gay"},{"pid":"1512e8e219d4123fbb6e6136b59d0e4baa7e2e71","tid":1961381,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:25:48.000Z","msg":"你搵我？"},{"pid":"bdf1431ed30fd41c5b21a03496a2f41833941d35","tid":1961381,"uid":49847,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b84f01632b287292f49f84ba1de0d7e793c2fc89","tid":1961381,"uid":333451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:24:45.000Z","msg":"Gay"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T18:26:35.000Z","msg":"你條$99000追蹤我咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji